{"tid":1239452,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"所有問問題既記者朋友入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-18T07:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T08:55:39.000Z","uid":44925,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d968abd62b2ef7117ab39db81bd3f22566817286","tid":1239452,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"唔好再問埋一堆<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾問題</span></span><br />\n佢落唔落台一定有人問 而且根本唔重要<br />\n<br />\n最重要係 收唔收返佢係12號講既 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴動定性</span><br />\n<br />\n會唔會承諾 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤銷檢控示威者</span><br />\n<br />\n會唔會同係太古墮樓既義士<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去太古廣場外獻花鞠躬道歉 </span><br />\n<br />\n你覺唔覺得你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">背負左一條人命</span><br />\n<br />\n點樣追究警方<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">使用過度武力</span> 例子:係中信外<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">向不反對通知書地區放催淚彈</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣向<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無警員編號警察</span>追究佢使用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">過度暴力 近乎殺人</span>??<br />\n<br />\n求下各位記者 唔係個個有機會問問題<br />\n唔好再浪費機會問堆垃圾問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed727764c34704609ac1935ec3caaea03b555956","tid":1239452,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"請大家幫推"},{"pid":"60e1ad1e19461f9d1222c98967d22319d988591d","tid":1239452,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"請大家幫推<br />\n推到記者睇到"},{"pid":"c5f064a5f57dfd30d48ff803540f09ab298d6f15","tid":1239452,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"請大家幫推<br />\n推到記者睇到"},{"pid":"b927824e3115bdf2c3c7d3cf44bc1cfbaec8a397","tid":1239452,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"請大家幫推<br />\n推到記者睇到"},{"pid":"26109f50fb711c22508f6c4a887a75bcd6ac657e","tid":1239452,"uid":44925,